  <description>Plants 25–50 cm. Leaves: petioles narrowly winged; blades obovate, 2.5–8 cm wide, margins remotely toothed, pinnately lobed, or entire (teeth not prominently white-tipped, apices obtuse), faces glabrous or glandular-hispid. Heads 10–30. Involucres 8–12 mm. Phyllaries lanceolate, apices acute, faces strongly or finely glandular-hispid. Cypselae brown, 3.5–5 mm, not beaked; pappi 4–8 mm. 2n = 22.</description>
